===Etymology 1===
Possibly a variant of {{m|en|Xenia}}, from {{der|en|la|Xenia}}, from {{der|en|grc|ξενία|t=hospitable}}, the assumed name of a fifth-century saint venerated in the [[Eastern Orthodox Church]], from {{m|grc|ξένος|t=foreign, strange}}.
